main_body:
The unit amounts referred to in Article 5 (1) (b) of Regulation (EEC) No 1443/82 in respect of the 1983/84 marketing year are hereby fixed as follows:
(a) the advance payment of the basic production levy for A sugar and B sugar shall be 0,535 ECU per 100 kilograms of white sugar;
(b) the advance payment of the B levy for B sugar shall be 10,026 ECU per 100 kilograms of white sugar;
(c) the advance payment of the basic production levy for A isoglucose and B isoglucose shall be 0,428 ECU per 100 kilograms of dry matter.
